title: Wilson's Tyra Ott is lehighvalleylive Girls Tennis Player of the Week
text:
Tyra Ott , Wilson Ott won her third straight District 11 Class AA singles championship on Monday. 
The junior defeated Notre Dame's Coco Chen in the the final for the second straight season. This time around she posted a 6-3, 6-4 victory to clinch the title. 
The defending state champion didn't lose a set the entire tournament. 
HONORABLE MENTION: Fr. Brenna Magliochetti , Bethlehem Catholic; So. Molly Ehrig , Bethlehem Catholic; Fr. Logan Lencheski , Notre Dame; Sr. Madelyn Conrad , Liberty; Sr. Samantha Peterson , Liberty; Fr. Natalie Sinai , Freedom, Jr. Kaitlyn Swint , Freedom; Jr. Madison Stewart , Nazareth; Fr. Halle DeNardo , Nazareth.
